{"title":"小汤山的天使","authors":["徐后纯"],"dates":[{"year":2003,"month":6,"day":25}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"小汤山的天使"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"徐后纯"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"SARS像一道血红的流星"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"划过春天的时空"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"顷刻间"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一场没有硝烟的战争展开"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"生与死的较量"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"生与死的抉择"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"考验着你"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我去，我去"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我是党员"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我是团员"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我是……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"以深沉、庄严的名义"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"交上一份一份"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"很重很重的请战书"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这里，小汤山"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"很静，很静——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"迎着一双双渴求生命的眼睛"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你从四面八方走来"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一腔热血化作一份份爱心"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"倾洒在雪白的病房"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"用青春的活力召唤着一个个生命"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"以坚强的信念感染着一个个迷茫的眼神"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"传播，感染"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"都不能淹没你瘦小的身影"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"恐惧，孤独"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"压不垮你刚强的身躯"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"从你的身上"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们感受到力量"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"和一种奉献精神"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"待到明天太阳升起时"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那是授给你的一枚闪光的勋章"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":9,"page_end":9}